snippet.title: C64 Longplay: Java Jim in Square Shaped Trouble (NTSC) (with on-screen guide)
snippet.description: This saves you reading the wall of text in my last upload. Phew! Immensely complicated to figure out but quite satisfying. I mapped it all out on Excel over three days. The game was also made for the Atari 800. The programmer, Rupert Bowater, had a thing for complexity as he also co-programmed Zoids for the C64 and Wicked for the Amiga. Zoids is another I've yet to solve...
